column4: NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "50BAB33941E3FDD8DBE349A6DB216D75", "Did you bring something to treat the wound?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "59CB294849881F266B622B82A8D8B526", "I hurt my wing. Do you got something to treat my wound?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "0ECAD5CA471FB05BEC4ACBA80FE6B89E", "It looks bad. Hold on. What should I do?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "452BD3B146627DC5BE15BC886A25BB6B", "I don\'t think I can fly far.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "B9944F824B9F727825D356BE2A7AF92C", "There\'s a clinic in city. You should go there. It isn\'t far from here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "4D37B7014BCF6C1082FBA9A16EEB65B8", "I heard about the city. It\'s bigger than I thought.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "B195AFAB43AFA62DF87B2EBD295B7C37", "Thanks. Maybe I can help you someday.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2FF67F5640DDC61DBF002397C015708B]", "1D7815D34396C379DC4A469F4423EE14", "I\'ll bring something to cure your wound. Wait for me.")
